{"word":"G1689 - ἐμβλέπω - emblépō - em-blep'-o - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμβλέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">emblépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em-blep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவனித்துப்பார், காண், பார்"},{"paragraph":"to turn one's eyes on; look at"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G991 - βλέπω - blépō - blep'-o/991\">G991</a>; to <i>look on</i>, that is, (relatively) to <i>observe</i> fixedly, or (absolutely) to <i>discern</i> clearly: - behold, gaze up, look upon, (could) see.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}